Structogram editor

Current state (development, not usable):
 * Class structure of statements and constructs implemented
 * General text output with XML-based syntax descriptor files
 * Structure for handling editing actions

Milestones:
 * Simple GUI interface with text view based on above mentioned syntaxes
   and complete support for editing, saving, loading algorithms and syntaxes.
 * Drag&Drop support in the text view for moving elements
 * Structogram view with
 * Drag&Drop support in the structogram view
 * Experiments with alternative controls for the structogram view.
   Example: "add box below" button on the bottom of said box
